ls from the Conservative politician Damian Collins that Zuckerberg appear b=
efore a select committee inquiry into fake news.She wrote to Collins: &quot=
;Facebook fully recognises the level of public and Parliamentary interest i=
n these issues and support your belief that these issues must be addressed =
at the most senior levels of the company by those in an authoritative posit=
ion to answer your questions. As such, Mr. Zuckerberg has personally asked =
one of his deputies to make themselves available to give evidence in person=
